Qn9U8IUArQWfVJkJjtGCQg2c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2-%E7%A7%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B1%82%E9%86%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E9%80%81%E5%A8%81%E9%99%A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR26P_HBLiEuz2bch0mju03JE5NRmT9XJ4yQn9U8IUArQWfVJkJjtGCQg2c&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1RSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=e075b053\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2-%E7%A7%81%E9%99%A2%E6%B1%82%E9%86%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E5%AE%89%E6%8E%92%E9%80%81%E5%A8%81%E9%99%A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR26P_HBLiEuz2bch0mju03JE5NRmT9XJ4yQn9U8IUArQWfVJkJjtGCQg2c&h=b12316d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/中大宿舍一女生疑曾到武漢-私院求醫被拒-衛生署安排送威院/?fbclid=IwAR26P_HBLiEuz2bch0mju03JE5NRmT9XJ4yQn9U8IUArQWfVJkJjtGCQg2c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌佢 明知要隔離仲通街走！"},{"pid":"37e18dde7963026472c604dedc742e5822f5de99","tid":1812462,"uid":65760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:10:40.000Z","msg":"所以有啲陰謀論話其實係特登由武漢帶來香港。<br />\n我有少少相信呢種講法，個時間點實在太夾，咁啱燉炳強大圍捕想嚇人唔出來，咁啱呢個時候又爆中國肺炎想啲人唔好去人多嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n世界上邊有咁多巧合"}]}